Looking for a New LA delicacy, eh?
Then you have to try my house special![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025305_MSG0002
rows.name:
It's the Calorie Bomber, a juicy hamburger with all the
trimmings, and it's just 700 credits![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025305_MSG0003
rows.name:
One Calorie Bomber, piping hot from the grill!
This is sure to knock the socks off your Ma-non friend.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025305_MSG0004
rows.name: You sure? Well, I'll be here if you change your mind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025305_MSG0005
rows.name: Uh, you don't seem to have 700 credits on you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025305_MSG0006
rows.name: Better go do your BLADE thing and earn a little scratch.[ST:wait ]
